{"product_id":"vielo-organic-body-lotion-refill-500ml","title":"Vielö Organic Body Lotion Refill 500ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic body lotion, specially designed to moisturise and soften dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), wheat germ oil (protecting), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), lavender (soothing) and sage (strengthening).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBy choosing sustainable refills you take good care of your skin and our planet.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to clean and dry skin. Massage in gently.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lactis Serum Proteinum **, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil **, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil **, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate \/ Stearate *, Cetyl Alcohol *, Glycerin **, Betaine *, Aqua *, Citric Acid *, Xanthan Gum *, Tocopherol *, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil **, Sodium Hyaluronate *, Potassium Sorbate, Salvia Officinalis Oil **, Citronellol ** \/ ***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil **, Geraniol ** \/ ***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate *, Arnica Montana Flower Extract **, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract **, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract **, Limonene ** \/ ***, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract **, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract **, Sodium Lactate *, Citral ** \/ ***.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (89,7%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901107507527,"sku":null,"price":70.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-body-lotion-refill-500ml-719231.jpg?v=1739897176","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/vielo-organic-body-lotion-refill-500ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}